The US forces are killing other humans. If you believe the government's twist on it, then it's for freedom. Why is freedom - a word used to describe a conceptual way of living - more important than God's will? If you're a Christian that understands the religion that you follow, then I can't possibly understand by any stretch why you'd say things like this.<br>
